    21	 program  that could scan the  libraries here on  CompuServe and winnow out
    22	 the good  stuff for  you?   Well, it  might not  freak _you_  out, but  it
    23	 _would_ freak my fiancee out (although I think  she believes that I've had
    24	 some sort of electronic implants already anyway).
    25	
    26	      Well,  at any rate, Thanksgiving is this coming week and Christmas is
